commit.message: Changed for loop variables to be more descriptive. Also fixed level number not updating when transitioning to next level
Added testing level. Access by pressing '0' in playscreen
Removed extra save that made you drop from the sky in level2
All save data now saved in save.p
Fixed leaving first level by jumping above start
Made exit doors larger to prevent going beyond end of level
Added testing mode where you dont have to build movement functions. To enter testing mode add 'test' on the commandline when running main
fixed merge conflict; added ToC to helpers
fixed merge conflict with import changes from kara
Saves now looking in correct directory
Fixed current level string displaying incorrectly
Removed all old and redundant code for exiting
Moved current level varaibles to player so that exiting by collision works
Added new exit code, not yet tested
